data.description: This two bedroom, 1.5 bathroom, 1 car garage is located conveniently down the road from Genesis-West Hospital and easy access to Marquette, Locust, Kimberly or Harrison Road.  Head through the front door into the main living room that features a wood burning stove and original hardwood floors.  The formal dining room has original hardwood floors and several windows that bring in natural light. Connected directly to the kitchen, you'll find updated appliances.  Downstairs you'll find a second living space, laundry space and a half bath.  Head upstairs and you'll notice the hardwood staircase that leads you to 2 bedrooms with original hardwood floors and a full bath. [Roof replaced in 2021, new boiler 2010, new AC capacitor 2020, new 100 amp panel 2010, HWH 1998]
